   ║
   ║  ─── KNOWN PRE-EXISTING ISSUES (flagged, NOT fixed in this pass) ───
   ║    • renderLinks() is defined TWICE. The second definition is a
   ║      copy of renderNotesWidget() and shadows the first one (JS
   ║      function-declaration hoisting — last wins). See section 24.
